doc_summary_long: Woman stabbed 32 times by ex-boyfriend marries first responder who rescued her When Melissa Dohme Hill was 20 years old, she received a call from her high school ex-boyfriend asking to meet up one last time to gain closure. When she arrived, he pulled out a switchblade, stabbed her 32 times and left her bleeding by the side of the road.
